Dialogs.Dialog: Can we solve this problem together?
Your confidence is wonderful. You're doing your best.
I was to do my best together so, from now on... let me next to you. I'm kidding.
Hey, the results of the math quiz――
I did perfect! Thanks to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲, for teaching me a lot!
I'm glad you thought you'd get good results.
You answered my questions fluently, and you were working hard...
Ah, no, what I was... That, you know... Let's do our best next time, right?
How can sensei come up with a surprising solution like that?
Oh, that. I came up with it during preparation.
The result of everyday efforts. That's right, it's amazing. I want to be an apprentice.
You're already one, ▲高嶺＊＊▲! I was just imitating you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Fufu! It's a little strange. Two people learning from each other.
Hey.... From now one, let's do our best while learning from each other, okay?
I wonder if I should solve it like this. I understand now. Okay, next problem?
Hmm. You've been studying with a smile on your face recently.
I'm doing excellent, maybe because you're with me.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, when you say that, it makes me want to do my best.
Me too. I'll do my best, if you tell me.
Perhaps, that is what make us give our best.
Of course! That's why... We will always be together, right?
That difficult problem, you're the only one who solved it.
Do you mean, you didn't solve it, ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
Hmm. Can I brag about it? I'm kidding.
Haha! If you brag about it, it's going to be more difficult, so please refrain from doing it...
But now, you can really solve any problem.
Should I brag about that instead?... I'm kidding.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Umm... why are you angry?
You did your best studying alone.
Hmm. It's because I want to be a man who deserves to be with you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Well done. I'll be with you next time, right?
（I did my best in Modern studies this time!）
Were you everyone's focus? Everyone said your interpretation was sharp.
Isn't it enough? I'm telling the truth.
If you say so, it was worth the effort.
Really? Then, I'll do it more! Is it okay?
If you do it too much... I'll be troubled!
Fufu~! Geez, don't say it like that.
You do your best because you're very nice. I'm kidding▼
What's wrong? You're sighing too much.
I couldn't concentrate on today's class. It's you fault, okay?
Did you guess it by saying it aloud?
You said it aloud, and your voice was wonderful... I was watching you all the time.
Eh!? You don't have to, I didn't do anything that nice.
It's amazing!! It looked like that to me.
Your essay has become very popular.
I'm glad I put so much effort.
Fufu. I became your fan too▼
For the essay... too! I'm kidding.
I will continue to support you with all my strength. Fufu!
（Okay, I'll do my best next time!）
▲主人公＊▲, you're doing great, right? I want your help.
Hmm. Reading comprehension, interpretation, memory and then...
I don't want the results of your hard work, I want to emulate your hard work.
You looks so cool when you're concentrated... Keep up the good work, okay?
I want to learn your sense.
I still have along way to go, but thank you.
Even though you do such wonderful works, you still have things to learn?
I like that kind of thing...
Hmm? I couldn't hear that, can you say it once more!
You don't have to polish that sense.... Geez.
Wow... Hey, did you make it?
I thought it was wonderful. I wanted to decorate my room.
Hmm. Hey, everyone can see it.
... Would you like to hide it? With you, for example.
Your work, all to yourself. I'm kidding.
（Okay, let's do out best next time!）
Your recent work is wonderful. Looking at it, warms my heart...
If you say it ▲高嶺＊＊▲, then it was worth the effort.
Fufu. You won't get anything is you lie.
But, I think it's really nice...
I want you to show me more, I'll always be next to you.
I like the recent paintings you draw.
Fufu, I'm serious. You deserve all the praise.
It reflects kindness and the use of colors is amazing...
Above all, I'm happy with that word.
Hmm, really. So, can you praise me more?
▲主人公＊▲. Did you see that photo? It's amazing.
Hey... What do you need to create such a wonderful thing?
How can I make that effort? With sense?
How!?... Do you want to know that much?
You may have been born with it, but there are ways to improve it...
It's all fine, because if this happens, you'll be the only one.
（I have to do my best next time!）
Are you popular now because you have a wonderful singing voice?
The truth is, I want to have only you for myself...
But I want to brag a little... Keep doing your best, okay?
Hmm. The sound is so clear... I want to listen to it many times.
Fufu! If that happens, should I play the piano too?
You were singing with so much intention, even sensei smiled!
I thought that music really makes you enjoys the sound.
I wonder if I sing with you, it'll feel good.
It was amazing. It seems that my knowledge of music is expanding.
It's a lot of fun because I can listen to Chopin and other composers.
I'll be left behind if I don't do my best.
...Fufu! But, you don't want to lose, right?
Even so, I'm a senior in music.
During music class, it looks like you're having so much fun and I get lured in.
I think it ▲高嶺＊＊▲ get lured, we can have a lot of fun.
It's ideal, and good results will follow.
I don't think we should have any trouble, when you're with me, ▲高嶺＊＊▲!
I also want to do my best because I have you...
Fufu. Let's continue like this, shall we do our best?
When you sing, I'm often told that you have a good face.
And you think that too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
Isn't it wonderful? Like a proud boyfriend!
... That's what it looks like. You looks so happy.
It's a little embarrassing ...but, it something that happens.
（It makes me shy... but I'm glad I did my best!）
You're doing amazing these days. You have good times for both short and long distances.
Thank you, maybe the waves are coming!
Hmm. Your running pose was so cool. It was really nice――
That is why... I love you?... I'm kidding.
I'm sorry, I couldn't hear it, can you say it again!
（Okay, let's do our best next time!）
Ah... Well, you look great and your body is in good shape.
Maybe my afforts are coming out!
You look so nice when you're in the court,
I would be glad if it was just normal.
I'm sorry. I was just thinking...
Please tell me your opinions after breaking records one after another.
There are still more, so I want to aim higher!
What do you have to do?
Then, the gold medal from me is still in the future, right?
I will give you a reward for your hard work.
Let's do out best without getting injured▼
（Okay, I have to do my best!）
（I did my best to exercise this time!）
Yo. Fufu! You're doing great, right?
I also secretly raise my nose. I'm kidding.
It's not a secret, it's okay to be proud!
Tell me if you get tired? I'll massage you. Okay?
What's wrong? ▲高嶺＊＊▲... You're staring at nothing.
Ah~, I'm sorry. Um... I think you're getting stronger...
So that's why, I was getting a little excited...
...Hmm. When you get closer, you can hear the sound of my heart...
Good work ▲高嶺＊＊▲... Hmm? You look happy.
Yes, because of your great success.
I know you're doing your best... I'm very happy.
Hmm. I think we can get good results in the game.
That is, you can do it too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲!
Fufu, yes. I'll do my best▼
You won the rally with president Tezuka, aren't you tired?
Everyone said it was amazing, right? I want to use your practices as reference.
But I still can't compete with you.
Shall we do our best? I'll help you too, right?
▲主人公＊▲. Did you finish cleaning up?
I knew it, I wish I had come a little earlier.
Fufu, geez. If it's a cleaning competition, I won't lose next time.
I wonder if I can help you next time. Well then, it's time to go home.
Good work. Shall we go home?
▲主人公＊▲. Hey, why did you go to that scene before?
Hmm. My body moved on it's own! It's a joke.
Fufu. It's not a joke, but something you wanted to do, right?
That's why I'm practicing so much... I'll be in the play.
Recently, you have been in many impressive scenes, and I...
（Hmm, I have to do my best next time!）
Your form... isn't it something beautiful?
Don't forget about your purpose. I'll be watching over you.
I'll help you. Take a step!
Really? Then, please... Should I do it?
Eh~, is it okay? Taking a step...
Fufu, I get it. I look forward to work with you, Coach▼
（First place in mixed classes relay. I wonder if ▲高嶺＊＊▲ saw）
You know, when you got first place...
I was yelling! You did it... I love you...
Oh, it's okay. It was just a little embarrassing...
But, I'm glad. You looked so cool getting first▼
You know, when... you looked so cool while swimming.
I'm kind of nervous. I wonder if it's because you only are wearing trunks. You look strong.
Hmm.... Fufu~. But, you look cool even if you don't swim▼
